Dependencies
=====================

  - itools (V 0.62)
  - ikaaro (V 0.62) (V iscrib -> http://git.hforge.org/?p=ikaaro.git;a=shortlog;h=refs/heads/iscrib)
  - lpod-python (V master)
  - itws (V master - itws 1.2 with shop functionnality - release to come)

Installation
=====================

 $ python setup.py install


Create a new instance
=======================

Initialize instance:

  $ icms-init.py iscrib.localhost

Set iscrib as a module

  $ vi iscrib.localhost/config.conf

    > + modules = iscrib
    > - modules =

Start instance:

  $ icms-start.py iscrib.localhost

Open firefox

  $ firefox http://localhost:8080/

Add a website

  $ firefox http://localhost:8080/;new_resource?type=WebSite

Your website is the demo website.
